OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773864689
OL,3,CBolton to bid for 'biggest ever' Ryder
OL,4,CCup
OL,6,FA bid to bring golf's Ryder Cup to
OL,7,FBolton could be boosted by the
OL,8,Fannouncement of a #70m road scheme.
OL,10,FPlans for a #240m Hulton Park resort
OL,11,Fis at the heart of the bid.
OL,13,FGreater Manchester Mayor Andy Burnham
OL,14,Fannounced the M61-M6 link road plan
OL,15,Fand said it could strengthen the bid
OL,16,Ffor a new golf course in Hulton Park
OL,17,Fto host the event in 2035.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
