OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773864689
OL,3,CBolton to bid for 'biggest ever' Ryder
OL,4,CCup
OL,6,FAndy Burnham, Mayor of Greater
OL,7,FManchester, said: "The success of the
OL,8,FBRIT Awards in Manchester shows that
OL,9,Fwe can we attract and deliver
OL,10,Finternational events to a brilliant
OL,11,Fstandard.
OL,13,F"Culture and sport will be major
OL,14,Fdrivers of our good growth, and that's
OL,15,Fwhy we're bidding to host the biggest
OL,16,Fever Ryder Cup in Bolton in 2035.
OL,18,F"We've had promising conversations
OL,19,Fwith organisers about bringing the
OL,20,Ftournament to a bespoke, world-class
OL,21,Fcourse at Hulton Park.
OL,26,@oD@SOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773864689
OL,3,CBolton to bid for 'biggest ever' Ryder
OL,4,CCup
OL,6,F"But it will only be possible with the
OL,7,Fright infrastructure. We're doing our
OL,8,Fbit to make it happen.
OL,10,F"We're committing up to #70 million to
OL,11,Fdeliver a transport package to not
OL,12,Fonly help spectators get to the site
OL,13,Fbut deliver major benefits for the
OL,14,Fpeople living in the surrounding
OL,15,Fareas."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
