OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773864689
OL,3,CBolton to bid for 'biggest ever' Ryder
OL,4,CCup
OL,6,FBolton Council initially rejected the
OL,7,Fproposal for the Hulton Park course
OL,8,Fciting environmental reasons, but it
OL,9,Fwas later approved by a government
OL,10,Finspector in 2022 after an appeal by
OL,11,Fdevelopers Peel L&P.
OL,13,FThe Hulton Park plan includes a luxury
OL,14,Fhotel, lodges and a health club, with
OL,15,Fthe course set to be built to
OL,16,Faccommodate 65,000 spectators.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
