PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773864689
OL,3,CBolton to bid for 'biggest ever' Ryder
OL,4,CCup
OL,6,FSouthport's Tommy Fleetwood,
OL,7,Fprofessional golfer and Ryder Cup
OL,8,Fwinner, said it would be "incredible"
OL,9,Fto bring "the biggest sporting event
OL,10,Fin the world" to the north-west of
OL,11,FEngland.
OL,13,FThe Ryder Cup, golf's biggest team
OL,14,Fcompetition, dates back to 1927.
OL,15,FWatched globally by millions, it's
OL,16,Fsaid to be the third biggest sporting
OL,17,Fevent in the world.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
