OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773864689
OL,3,CBolton to bid for 'biggest ever' Ryder
OL,4,CCup
OL,6,FClubs in Merseyside and Lancashire,
OL,7,Fnamely Royal Lytham & St Annes and
OL,8,FRoyal Birkdale, have hosted the event,
OL,9,Fbut it hasn't been staged in Greater
OL,10,FManchester before.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
